{"tid":426042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 有冇巴絲多愁善感鍾意創作?","createTime":"2017-10-06T09:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T15:20:09.000Z","uid":62225,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b527faf171ffd43f47725208259316df093fc78a","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:13:03.000Z","msg":"如果有個關於創作、製作嘅workshop，你會想聽或者學啲咩?<br />\n<br />\n事關今次我哋搵咗好有經驗同貼地嘅兩位分享人： <br />\n朱鳳嫻（全方位獨立創作女演員／編劇／電影導演） <br />\n鄺神<br />\n同大家你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真，之前都有搞同類workshop &amp; 分享會，巴絲出到嚟嘅feedback都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分享會會喺下星期五 7:30pm舉行，大致內容係： <br />\n1. 由微電影走向大電影 <br />\n2. 跨媒體創作分享 <br />\n3. 創作意念、層次、技巧 <br />\n4. 精華片段摘要及分析 <br />\n5. 你問我答互動創作交流 <br />\n6. 短片放映 <br />\n<br />\n大家可以到時嚟交流一吓~ 歡迎有興趣嘅巴絲報名： <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc05zapIdcptmh5X-7moqxTfoMhU9PmdLz6AG9D4NsEvhan7w/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc05zapIdcptmh5X-7moqxTfoMhU9PmdLz6AG9D4NsEvhan7w%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=ozqclEHD6SjlxRPgK5trzo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=de15c6bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc05zapIdcptmh5X-7moqxTfoMhU9PmdLz6AG9D4NsEvhan7w/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"d5f1030eb3091433a2e271879989c5b417496b45","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9173982064c49d2da45690be681759f31f18a9b","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d26a1228cad78edb6d878244ef563598c97956","tid":426042,"uid":35370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港搞創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你整到完美作品<br />\n否則無論如何都係比人小到一文不值<br />\n一係就得幾丁友圍爐打飛機 小圈子互相吹捧<br />\n外國會搞到嘅，香港搞呢啲根本就係吃力不討好<br />\n我至憎就係喺香港搞創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed7a7b2a74e71c89a447296c90f4c41f3191c0c","tid":426042,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"鄺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"4fdaad457ee352706c1f9cd9ab9bdf01a7a23359","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港搞創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你整到完美作品<br />\n否則無論如何都係比人小到一文不值<br />\n一係就得幾丁友圍爐打飛機 小圈子互相吹捧<br />\n外國會搞到嘅，香港搞呢啲根本就係吃力不討好<br />\n我至憎就係喺香港搞創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我相信你講出咗好多想做創作嘅青少年心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n實在見到好多有才華嘅人係香港冇好大嘅空間發揮，好多都會將出路揀去外國、台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個問題或者當日我都可以帶去問問嘉賓，睇下佢哋有咩見解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b871d2467edb9bf3cc83ebb653b61e057c505a40","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5929ef01d39c372a68d8ad07c9ac3ac89bd998a","tid":426042,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"075b7af32b8f84bfa0c4f2ab5d1f87cfe668e59a","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52040525f970fae574adfb56264fb9c6a16cdc1","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93958322304575184c7acbbeeb7d4c9e1153e44e","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062f1b5736b9878284daea6b12a1a818390b0ccb","tid":426042,"uid":62225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcd802ea927d494bb405ae78cf6aa64eb5471c1","tid":426042,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"撞左有其他野做...會唔會有其他機會可以了解多啲？"}]}